msgid "SWSTRING"
msgstr "Only available in the registered version"

msgid "DOSY"
msgstr "(Press Y to quit)"

msgid "QUITMSG1"
msgstr ""
"Please don't leave, there's more\n"
"demons to toast!"

msgid "QUITMSG2"
msgstr ""
"Let's beat it—this is turning\n"
"into a bloodbath!"

msgid "QUITMSG3"
msgstr ""
"I wouldn't leave if I were you.\n"
"DOS is much worse."

msgid "QUITMSG4"
msgstr ""
"You're trying to say you like DOS\n"
"better than me, right?"

msgid "QUITMSG5"
msgstr ""
"Don't leave yet—there's a\n"
"demon around that corner!"

msgid "QUITMSG6"
msgstr ""
"Ya know, next time you come in here\n"
"I'm gonna toast ya."

msgid "QUITMSG7"
msgstr "Go ahead and leave. see if I care."

msgid "QUITMSG8"
msgstr ""
"You want to quit?\n"
"Then, thou hast lost an eighth!"

msgid "QUITMSG9"
msgstr ""
"Don't go now, there's a \n"
"dimensional shambler waiting\n"
"at the DOS prompt!"

msgid "QUITMSG10"
msgstr ""
"Get outta here and go back\n"
"to your boring programs."

msgid "QUITMSG11"
msgstr ""
"If I were your boss, I'd \n"
"deathmatch ya in a minute!"

msgid "QUITMSG12"
msgstr ""
"Look, bud. you leave now\n"
"and you forfeit your body count!"

msgid "QUITMSG13"
msgstr ""
"Just leave. When you come\n"
"back, I'll be waiting with a bat."

msgid "QUITMSG14"
msgstr ""
"You're lucky I don't smack\n"
"you for thinking about leaving."

msgid "QUITMSG15"
msgstr ""
"Where are you going?!\n"
"What about the rebellion?"

msgid "QUITMSG16"
msgstr ""
"Carnage interruptus…\n"
"What a tease!"

msgid "QUITMSG17"
msgstr ""
"But you're the hope\n"
"—my only chance!!"

msgid "QUITMSG18"
msgstr "Nobody walks out on Blackbird."

msgid "QUITMSG19"
msgstr "I thought you were different…"

msgid "QUITMSG20"
msgstr "Fine! just kill and run!"

msgid "QUITMSG21"
msgstr ""
"You can quit…\n"
"but you can't hide…"

msgid "QUITMSG22"
msgstr ""
"Whaaa, what's the matter?\n"
"Mommy says dinnertime?"

msgid "QUITMSG23"
msgstr ""
"Don't quit now, there are still\n"
"flemoids on the loose!"

msgid "QUITMSG24"
msgstr ""
"Don't give up—the flemoids will\n"
"get the upper hand!"

msgid "QUITMSG25"
msgstr ""
"Don't leave now.\n"
"We need your help!"

msgid "QUITMSG26"
msgstr ""
"I hope you're just taking a\n"
"break for Chex® party mix."

msgid "QUITMSG27"
msgstr ""
"Don't quit now!\n"
"We need your help!"

msgid "QUITMSG28"
msgstr ""
"Don't abandon the\n"
"Intergalactic Federation of Cereals!"

msgid "QUITMSG29"
msgstr ""
"The real Chex® Warrior\n"
"wouldn't give up so fast!"

